<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>يُحِبُّ مَوْلاكَ حُسْنُ الْخُلُقِ مُقْتَرِنًا<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>بِالْجُودِ لَمْ يَبْقِيَا لِلذَّنْبِ مِنْ أَثَرِ<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>إِنَّ السَّخِيَّ حَبِيبٌ لِلإِلَهِ لَهُ<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>قُرْبٌ مِنَ اللهِ هَذَا جَاءَ فِي الْخَبَرِ<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>وَلا تَرُحْ بِلَئِيمٍ سَرْحَ عَارِضَةٍ<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>تَرِدْ بِهِ فِي ظَمَا مِنْ حَافَةِ النَّهْرِ<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>وَلا تَغُرَّنْكَ مِنْهُ طُولَ مِكْنَتِهِ<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span>حَلْفَاءَ عَارٍ بِلا ظِلٍّ وَلا ثَمَرِ<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span>بَذْلُ النَّفِيسِ عَلَى نَفْسِ الْخَسِيسِ عَنًا<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span>فِعْلُ الْجَمِيلِ لَدَيْهُ مُوجِبُ الضَّرَرِ<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span>وَمَنْ يَؤُمُّ لَئِيمًا عِنْدَ حَاجَتِهِ<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span>يَعُضُّ كَفَّيْهِ كَالْكُسْعِي وَسْطَ قرِي<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span>وَاسْلُكْ سَبِيلَ كِرَامٍ أَصْفِيَاءٍ مَضَوْا<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span>بِكُلِّ حَمْدٍ عَلَى الآفَاقِ مُنْتَشِرِ<a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p15"></span>وَاحْذَر طَبَائِعَ أَهْلِ اللَّوْمِ إِنَّ لَهُمْ<a href="#p15" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p16"></span>ذَمًا يُدُومُ عَلَى الآصَالِ وَالْبُكْرِ<a href="#p16" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p17"></span>وَاغْنَمْ مَكَارِمَ تُبْقِيهَا مُخَلَّدَةٌ<a href="#p17" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p18"></span>فِي أَلْسُنِ النَّاسِ مِنْ بَدْوٍ وَمِنْ حَضَرِ<a href="#p18" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p19"></span>فَخَيْرُ فِعْلِ الْفَتَى فِعْلٌ يُبَلِّغُهُ<a href="#p19" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p20"></span>مِنَ الْمَحَامِدِِ مَا يُبْقَى عَلَى الأَثَرِ<a href="#p20" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p21"></span>فَالْمَرْءُ يَفْنَى وَيَبْقَى الذِّكْرُ مِنْ حَسَنٍ<a href="#p21" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p22"></span>وَمِنْ قَبِيحٍ فَخُذْ مَا شِئْتَهُ وَذَرِ<a href="#p22" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>